select employeename, basepay from sf_public_salaries
where jobtitle LIKE 'Captain%'

-- After reviewing the dataset, I wanted to create a view where I would only have the police captains of the San Francisco Police Department.
-- Since we had to find the base pay for each captain, I selected 'basepay' and used LIKE to only find the Captains. 

Link: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/9972-find-the-base-pay-for-police-captains?code_type=3
